<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> sarvvalokasamutpa</hi>tti (tti)<hi rend="grantha">sthi</hi>ti<hi rend="grantha">saṁhārakāra<unclear>ṇa</unclear>m <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śāsa</hi>na<hi rend="grantha">m śāśva</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ta<hi rend="grantha">m śambho<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīvrīhivṛti</hi>vā<hi rend="grantha">si</hi>na<hi rend="grantha">ḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ādicaṇḍeśvar<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice>jñe</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">m</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nam <hi rend="grantha">bhakta</hi> r malaimaṇṭalat
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tu tāḻaikkuṭi centapirāṉ p<unclear>e</unclear>yāṉāṉa yātavarāyaṉukku namaṭukkaḷaipuṟam teṉ(ka)
<lb n="4" break="no"/>karaināṭṭuc caturaputukkuḷa<supplied reason="omitted">m</supplied> muṉpu maṟṟāṉāyapporuta Avaṉinārāyaṇa- <hi rend="grantha">brahmā</hi> tarāya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉpakkal vilaikoṇṭu tāṉ Aṉu<hi rend="grantha">bha</hi> vittup potukiṟa Ikkuḷam nā <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ttāle
<lb n="6"/>Uṭaikuḷa(m)māyk kiṭantu kāṭuveṭṭi kaṭṭai paṟittu piṉpaṭṭu pirampeṟip
<lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>pa</unclear>yiṟceytu pontamaiyil Ikkuḷattukku muṉpu nam variyilār taraviṉ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>paṭi Accu patiṉālu Ikkuḷattukku Iṟai paṟṟāmai kaḻittu <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="9"/>nikki <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Āṇṭācaṟuti yuḻutukoṇṭu pontamaiyil Ikkuḷa<supplied reason="omitted">ttu</supplied>kku canti
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rātittavaṟ celvatāka nam makaṉār virapāṇṭiyatevarkku Eṭṭāvatu mutal I
<lb n="11" break="no"/>kkuḷattukku vāṭāk kaṭamaiyāka Āṇṭu Oṉṟukku <unclear>kaḻa</unclear>ñcāka nam variyilār taraviṉ
<lb n="12"/>paṭi naṅkarevaṇavarvacaṅ kuṭukka Ippaṭikku Aruḷāḷa<hi rend="grantha">brahmacakra</hi> vatti Eḻuttu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
